    "prompt": "<div class=\"qti-layout-row\"> <div class=\"qti-layout-col12\"> <div class=\"prompt\"> <p class=\"dap_body\">​Consecutive terms of a sequence have the values&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"6\"><math alttext=\"6\"><semantics><mn>6</mn><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>,&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\"><semantics><mn>2</mn><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>,&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"negative 2\"><math alttext=\"negative 2\"><semantics><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>, and&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"negative 6\"><math alttext=\"negative 6\"><semantics><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>. Of the following, which describes the sequence?</p> </div> </div> </div>\n",
    "answer": "A-63244",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​The terms could be part of an arithmetic sequence with a common difference of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"negative 4\"><math alttext=\"negative 4\"><semantics><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>.</p>",
        "value": "A-63244"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​The terms could be part of&nbsp;a geometric sequence with a common difference of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"negative 4\"><math alttext=\"negative 4\"><semantics><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>.</p>",
        "value": "B-63245"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​​​The terms could be part of&nbsp;an arithmetic sequence with a common ratio of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"negative 4\"><math alttext=\"negative 4\"><semantics><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>.</p>",
        "value": "C-63246"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​​​The terms could be part of&nbsp;a geometric sequence with a common ratio of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"negative 4\"><math alttext=\"negative 4\"><semantics><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>.</p>",
